          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Điện thoại:</strong><br />
            <a href="tel:+84389023720">0389.023.720</a> (Mr. Huy)<br />
            <a href="tel:+84353839500">0353.839.500</a> (Nhà sách Long Hưng)
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong><br />
            <a href="mailto:kinhdoanh@vpplonghung.com">kinhdoanh@vpplonghung.com</a><br />
            <a href="mailto:hotro@vpplonghung.com">hotro@vpplonghung.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Social Media -->
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3 class="footer-title">Theo dõi</h3>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a
            href="https://web.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61580711382370"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            title="Facebook"
            aria-label="Facebook"
          >
            <img src="/images/icon-social-facebook.webp" alt="" class="social-icon" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
