          đầu ngày 09/12/2020
        </p>
        <p class="text-small">
          <strong>Địa chỉ đăng ký:</strong> Số nhà LK03-07, Khu đô thị thấp tầng
          Roman Plaza Hải Phát, đường Tố Hữu, Phường Đại Mỗ, Thành phố Hà Nội,
          Việt Nam
        </p>
        <p class="text-small">
          <strong>Người đại diện:</strong> Ông Đinh Quang Dương — Chức vụ: Giám
          đốc
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="copyright">
        <a
          href="http://online.gov.vn/searchProfile/IndexTimKiem?btnRadioSearch=search-name-all&KeySearch=0109448311"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="gov-badge"
          aria-label="Đã thông báo Bộ Công Thương"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/thongbaoBCT.webp"
            alt="Đã thông báo Bộ Công Thương"
            width="160"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.classList.add('gov-badge--fallback')"
          />
        </a>
        <p class="text-small">
          &copy; 2026 Văn Phòng Phẩm Long Hưng. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: var(--color-brown);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .footer-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .footer-title {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .footer-text {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .footer-links.footer-links--compact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .footer-links.footer-links--compact li {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--color-gold-light);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-info a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 46px;
    height: 46px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 0;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    position: relative;
  }

  .social-icon {
    display: block;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
    color: var(--color-brown);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .footer-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .legal-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .text-small {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .copyright {
    text-align: right;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .gov-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: clamp(120px, 18vw, 160px);
    min-height: 46px;
    max-width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .gov-badge img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .gov-badge.gov-badge--fallback {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.5rem;
  }

  .gov-badge.gov-badge--fallback::after {
    content: "Da thong bao Bo Cong Thuong";
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0 var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .copyright {
      text-align: left;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .footer-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .text-small {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
